data.description: NO HOA's !!!!!! 3 bedroom , 2 bath corner lot home located in Mulberry, Florida near everything. This home sits on .31 of an acre in a small cul-de-sac in Imperial Lakes. This home has a lot of character with a built in stone fireplace, wood cathedral ceilings in the living room and a 2 car garage. Minutes from shopping and restaurants.
